        "title": "Our Story ",
        "body": "<p>At Ucore, we recognise just how essential mobile phones are when it comes to staying connected.</p><p>However, you’re typically required to hold the phone to answer calls and, if you’re expecting an important call, you’ll constantly be checking your device. </p><p>Understanding how frustrating it can be to miss urgent calls, the Ucore team created an innovative solution.</p><p>Our stylish hoodies feature a central pocket on the garment’s upper torso where mobile phones can be safely stored when playing sports, hitting the gym or just as you’re going about your daily life.   </p><p>Due to its sensitive location, as soon as a call connects to your phone, you’ll feel the vibrations and be able to promptly answer - meaning you don’t need to worry about missing any important messages</p>",
